二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required TextsFinancial Accounting, by Weygandt, Kieso, & Kimmel, IFRS. 3rd., 2015.
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources


三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程教學內容涵括基本之財務報表編製過程，目的在使修習者藉由熟悉此一程序，得以瞭解財務報表資訊之意義，從而應用於相關之決策制訂。本課程係商學教育之入門課程，為商學院同學日後深造、就業皆不可缺之基礎知識與能力。 


The course content includes the basic process to prepare financial statement. This course aims to enable the practitioners to understand the financial information and to apply in the relevant decision making by making them be familiar with the process to prepare financial statement. This course is the fundamental course of the Business Program and essential for pursuing further degrees and having employment in the future. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description一.課程進度與教學內容1. Accounting in Action (CH.1)2. The Recording Process (CH.2)3. Adjusting the Accounts (含 Appendix 3A)(CH.3)4. Completing the Accounting Cycle (CH.4)5. Accounting for Merchandising Operations (含 Appendix5A、5B)(CH.5)6. Inventories (含 Appendix6A、6B)(CH.6)7. Fraud,Internal Control and Cash (CH.7) 8. Accounting for Receivables (CH.8)(1)105學年度第1學期講授，但不列入考試範圍：  (a)CH.3 Page 102 Accural vs. Cash-Basis Accounting  (b)CH.4 Page 184~186 Appendix4A: Reversing Entries  (c)CH.5 Page 330~338 Fraud and Internal Control(2)105學年度第1學期不講授，且不列入考試範圍：  (a)CH.1 Page 27~28 Appendix 1A:Accounting Career Opportunities  (b)CH.3 Page 128~130 Appendix 3B:Concepts in Action  (c)CH.6 Page 293 Analysis:Using Inventory Turnover  (d)CH.6 Page 298~300 Appendix 6C:LIFO Inventory Method  (e)CH.8 Page 401 Analysis二.作業方式:每章指定作業三.考評及成績計算方式 1.平時考(1/3)：含小考成績、作業及課堂參與等 2.期中考(1/3)：CH.1~4 (考試日期另行公佈) 3.期末考(1/3)：CH.5~8 (考試日期另行公佈)四.缺課次數達本科上課總時數四分之一以上者，學業總成績一律不及格。缺課次數在四分之一以內者，酌扣   學業總成績二至十分。


